From wishes that come alive to moments that feel like a fairytale, and gifts that light up every heart, we’re here to make your holiday season unforgettable. 🎁💄

Here’s to a Merry Christmas & holiday season that’s truly #WrappedInMagic! ❄️

#Colorbar #MadeForMagic #Christmas #MerryChristmas

When the house of sin calls out to its vices, there’s no way you can resist the urge. 😈🖤

Why? Because it was a place where Lazy Gal puts you under a relaxing spell, life’s most tempting pleasures are satiated with Hungry Doll and losing yourself in temptation with Femme Fatale is a way of life. This and so much more unfolded at the Cosmopolitan Blogger Awards ‘24-25, the most sinful afternoon of 2024. 💄💋

Catch the fashion and the fun because the awards were all about magic. And then some. 🌟

#HouseOfSin

#CosmoBloggerAwards #Colorbar #ColorbarAtCosmo #Cosmopolitan #Blogger

What a magical journey it has been! 🎉 

From pioneering bold innovations to setting trends that empower you to express your magic, it has been an exciting 20 years! With every shade, every product, and every moment, we've strived to bring the best to you, because our consumers are at the heart of everything we do. 💄✨ 

There is real magic in the world and you are the real magicians ✨

Here’s to long-lasting, smudge-proof bond and magic!  #MayTheMagicBeWithYou #MadeForMagic

When @samirmodi, the Minister of Magic himself, graced the stage at the Cosmopolitan Blogger Awards, it wasn’t just about awards—it was about honouring excellence and celebrating talent. 🌟

Colorbar takes pride in showcasing emerging makeup artists and creators, offering them a platform to thrive and shine in collaboration with the #CosmopolitanBloggerAwards. 💄✨

Congratulations to all the incredible winners who are making waves in the world of beauty:
✨ Colorbar North Emerging Makeup Artist of the Year: @iamsahillllll
✨ Colorbar West Emerging Makeup Artist of the Year: @artistpoojabudhraja
✨ Colorbar East Emerging Makeup Artist of the Year: @makeupartist_prasenjit
✨ Colorbar South Emerging Makeup Artist of the Year: @parulkhattarmakeupartist
✨ LGBTQIA+ Makeup Artist of the Year: @cocoballucci_
✨ Celebrity Makeup Artist of the Year: @savleenmanchanda
✨ Artistry Makeup Artist of the Year: @alina_hasan_rizvi
